data.description: Get the location, city, country, lat/long etc of any IP address
data.name: Any IP

data.description: Get an IP's country name in a different language. 5 languages are currently supported i.e. English - en, German - de, French - fr, Japanese - ja and Simplified Chinese -zh-CN. The response will contain an ASCII encoded version of the country name in the language you specify.
data.name: Multi-language support
